<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Privacy Policy | EduSmart Academy</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.1/font/bootstrap-icons.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body class="bg-light py-5">
    <div class="container py-5">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-lg-9 text-center mb-5">
                <a href="/" class="btn btn-outline-primary rounded-pill mb-4 px-4 fw-bold shadow-sm">
                    <i class="bi bi-house-door-fill me-2"></i> Dashboard Home
                </a>
                <h1 class="display-3 fw-bold text-main">Privacy Policy</h1>
            </div>

            <div class="col-lg-10">
                <div class="card border-0 shadow-lg p-5 rounded-4 bg-white">
                    <div class="row g-5">
                        <div class="col-12">
                            <h3 class="fw-bold mb-4 text-primary h5 text-uppercase small">1. Data Storage</h3>
                            <p class="text-muted lh-lg">EduSmart Academy collects and securely stores administrative, academic, and personal data solely for institutional management. All data is stored in encrypted MongoDB databases.</p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="col-12 bg-light p-4 rounded-3 text-dark border-start border-primary border-4">
                            <h3 class="fw-bold mb-4 h5 small text-uppercase">2. Cookies & Session Integrity</h3>
                            <p class="text-muted lh-lg mb-0 opacity-75">We use essential institutional cookies (`school.sid`) to maintain secure authenticated sessions. These cookies are critical for identity verification and prevent unauthorized access.</p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="col-12">
                            <h3 class="fw-bold mb-4 text-primary h5 text-uppercase small">3. Information Protection</h3>
                            <p class="text-muted lh-lg">Administrative staff have limited, role-based access to user information. Personal contact details (emails, phone numbers) are never shared with external entities.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="mt-5 text-center small text-muted">
                        &copy; 2026 EduSmart Academy. Managed Security.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
